created_at.description: Timestamp of when the business unit is created, specified in the date-time format.

deleted.description:
Specifies whether the business unit is still a valid business function in the organization.
Possible values: true, false

description.description: Description stating what the business function entails.

id.description: Identifier of the business unit object, auto-generated when a new business unit is created in the Freshteam system.

name.description:
Descriptive identifier of the business unit.
Examples: Dev Ops, Web Ops, Engineering, and so on.

updated_at.description: Timestamp of when the business unit’s details were last modified, specified in the date-time format.
